snippet.title: The King of Fighters 2000 playthrough (PS2) (1CC)
snippet.description:
60fps available!

Playthrough with the Fatal Fury team. Originally KoF 2000 was released in Japan by itself for the PS2. America and Europe got a better deal as the game came as part of a two pack alongside KoF2001. This version of the game has some extra strikers you can unlock.
